sentences: Shin Ji-hoon (Hangul: 신지훈; born June 23, 1998) is a South Korean singer, actress and figure skater.
She was signed under Cube Entertainment and Starline Entertainment.
She is known as TOP 6 of SBS's K-pop Star Season 2.
From 2017, Shin Ji-hoon became an individual singer.
